article_title: Rep. Renee Ellmers breaks with GOP on immigration votes
article_text: Rep. Renee Ellmers of North Carolina was one of 10 Republicans who voted with Democrats on Wednesday against legislation that would roll back President Barack Obama’s executive actions on immigration.
